title: Dos Segundos Cantina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cozy Mexican restaurant with vegan brunch options, vegan beef in tacos, burritos and other items, along with smoked tofu and vegan beef fajitas and vegan desserts. Specials usually include a vegetarian or vegan option and all cruelty-free options are marked on the menu.
